Package: wch-ble-extcap
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: DC0SK <simon.keimer@mailbox.org>
Homepage: https://github.com/dc0sk/wireshark-extcap-wch-ble
Depends: libudev1
Recommends: wireshark
Description: Wireshark extcap plugin for the WCH BLE Analyzer Pro
 Captures Bluetooth Low Energy advertising traffic from the WCH (QinHeng
 Electronics) BLE Analyzer Pro dongle and presents it to Wireshark as a live
 capture interface, using DLT_BLUETOOTH_LE_LL_WITH_PHDR.
 .
 The dongle enumerates as three independent radios behind an internal hub.
 The plugin opens all three and assigns advertising channels 37, 38 and 39 one
 per radio, so the default "All channels" mode covers the full advertising
 band in a single capture.
 .
 A udev rule granting the logged-in user access to the dongle is installed
 alongside the plugin; no root privileges are needed to capture.
